href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/artemis3.bmp></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Artemis' temple</span><hr size=1> * Artemis is laying upon her bed of silks in he rlarge bedchamber on Olympus, suddenly she hears the roar of Dawn, one of the Amazons of Themiscrya, she puts down her book and vanishes in a burst of green light~<br>
<br>
~She reappears before Dawn in a green flash dressed in her long flowing white gown, her auburn locks flow free down her back, she looks to the Amazon~<br>
<br>
Is everything allright Dawn?<br>
<br>
~ A look of utter concern is on her face ~<br>
<br>
 <p>Goddess Artemis
Protector of the Amazons
~*~Goddess of the hunt and the Moon~*~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 119<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/4/01 12:20:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Everything alright.</span><hr size=1>  The tiger stood, shaking its fur and finally shifting to its human form. Dawn stretched abit as the priestesses gasp at the change. See there was nothing to fear of just a tiger, Dawn was another thing coming though. She turned at looked at Artemis.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Infact there is something wrong. The Amazons don't need all these gods leaving bribes for us, so that we will worship them. Its our choice to worship whom we want, and I think all of us would be alot happier if you asked Posiedon to stop. He's just bribing us, and trying to get Del. Its not helping us any.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Emerald orbs looked at Artemis, hoping she got her point across, as Artemis was the protector of the Amazons. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/4/01 6:52:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/artemis3.bmp></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Artemis' temple</span><hr size=1> ~ a soft smile fell across the Goddess's lips~ My dear Dawn, do not worry about it, just ignore my uncle.<br>
<br>
You are right, You all have the right to choose who you wish to worship. He is only making himself look like the ass he now seems to be. His true color is showing through, and his pettiness. I have spoken to Zeus and I am sure he will speak to Hera.<br>
<br>
As for DeL, nothing will happen to her, she has spoken with Hera and Hera will protect her should anything come about.<br>
<br>
Please dear Dawn, just ignore my uncle and his bribes. He may be older then I, but he is apparently very petty. <br>
I can talk my head off to my uncle and he willnot listen to me. He seems to think he is on a higher horse then us all...~shrugs~ just hang in there Dawn, it will all end soon...I hope...<br>
 <p>Goddess Artemis
Protector of the Amazons
~*~Goddess of the hunt and the Moon~*~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 122<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/4/01 7:55:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A thank you</span><hr size=1>  Dawn nodded lightly as she listened to the Goddess, she smiled as she ended. <br>
<br>
 &quot;Thank you Artemis, for just protecting us, and standing up for us. I thought I'd give it a try, and make it an effort to see my sisters happy again. &quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn gave a short Amazon salute, and then shifted back to her demonic tiger form. She then turned and padded out of the temple. Satisfied with what little help she recieved. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=57.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=54.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=53.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=53.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=53.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=53.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazon